      <title>喷洒在植物上的粘性油可以替代农药</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2430801-sticky-oil-sprayed-onto-plants-offers-alternative-to-pesticides/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
