      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2430295-pigs-seem-less-stressed-if-their-barn-is-scented-with-lavender/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
